And.label: And
And.documentation: Performs a logical conjunction on two expressions.

Mod.label: Mod
Mod.documentation: Divides two integers and returns the integer remainder.

Not.label: Not
Not.documentation: Performs logical negation on an expression.

Or.label: Or
Or.documentation: Performs a logical disjunction on two expressions.

Xor.label: Xor
Xor.documentation: Performs a logical exclusion on two expressions.
